'''SAINT TIMOTHY''' 
Timot Greek bhaxen ‘ Timontheos’ mhollear devak man divpi vo devan man favo  kel’lo.

== '''Tacho zolm''' ==

Bhag timot poilea xekdiant Ephesus xaracho poilo [[Kristanvponn|Kristi]] Bishop zalo.Bhag Timotacho zolm c . A.D 17 vorsa zalo, to Lycaonian xarant Lystra Asia Minor hanga vaddlo.

=== Avoy Bapuy ===

Tachea avoychem nanv Eunice ani Bapaychem nanv Lois, tim dhorman Judev aslem.Punn Timotacho bapui Greek axilo.

== '''Bhurgeponn''' ==

Bhurgeponna taun taka povitr dhormgrontachi vollok mell’li.Lhanponnim taun to soimban  unno ulovpi ani bizudd axilo, ani to bogor- bogor duenth zatallo.

== '''Tachem jivit''' ==

Bhag .Paulu aplea poilia dhormprocharok yatrek Barnabasa borobor Lysra desant ailo tedna tannem  eka zolma taun apangul monxak boro kelo dekun thoisorlea zaitiea lokhanim tachi xikvon  mannun ghetle.Bhag. Pauluchea dusrea  dhormprocharok yatrek Silasa borobor to Lystra ailo tednna Timotichea bapayn taka Bhag.Pauluxi vhello.Bhag .Timot Bhag Paulucho xis ani upranth dhor xikvonn diunk tacho sangatti zalo.52 hea vorsa, Bhag Paulu, Silasa ani Timot Macedonia xarant gele.
Timot ani Silasa Beroeanea xarant raule,ani uprant Corinth xarant gele.Tanchem hem jivit birankull ani koxttani borlelem.Punn devan taka aple utor xipdaunk apoilolo.Bhag Paulun ani poile Kristi Bishopani, Bhag. Timotak Ephesus xarachim zobabdari dili ani  taka tea xaracho bishop mhonn makhlo.

=='''Tacho sobhav'''==

Soimban to unnem ulovpi ani bizudd aslo. To bizudd assunui Bhag Paulun taka Korint  xarant daddlo tancho bhavarth ghott korunk.Taka ghombir velar pasun xantin vagpacho gunn axilo. Bhag Timotichenm nanv novea korarant zaitia chittinim mell’ta.



