== '''Koxxt ani moronn''' ==

Ithihas amkam sangta 97 hea vorsa, Bhag Timotin Macedonia xarant Devi Diana-chea manak zatalem tem pursav adailem ani xhub vortoman porgotunk suru kelem.Jednam tannem xubvortoman porgottunk suru kelem tednam tea murti- pujariani taka khub tras kele, taka khub marlo ani taka rostea velian voddit voddit vhorun taka xekim fatrani jivexhi marlo. Jednam taka hem koxxtachem moronn ailem tednam taka 79-80 vorsa asheli.

== '''Altaracho man''' ==

Taka Povitr Sobha ek Apostle, ek Bhagevonth ani ek Rogth xakxim mhonn  manta. 4 tea xekdianth tachi kudd (Constantinope Holy Apostles Church) hanga hadle.

